import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { artistasServices } from 'src/app/services/artistasServices'; @Component({ selector: 'app-info', templateUrl: './info.component.html', styleUrls: ['./info.component.css'] }) export class InfoComponent { artistas: Artistas[] = [ ]; constructor(private artistasService: artistasServices) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.artistasService.signArtists(this.id).subscribe (){ } } } export interface Artistas { idArtista: number, nombreArtista: string, fechaDeRegistro: string, estiloMusical: string, correo: string, telefono: number, nombreAKA: string, mensaje: string, aceptarTerminos: boolean }
